data.description: Brick Front center hall colonial Featuring possible 5 bedrooms on the second floor and 1 additional bedroom on the first floor. This spacious home offers a Beautiful living room/dining room with Hardwood Floors, and a Great Two Story Family Room off the Kitchen. Full Kitchen includes loads of cabinets , Granite Counters, Two Stainless Steel Wall Ovens, a Gas Cook Top, Breakfast Nook and a Butlers Pantry. Lots of Recessed lighting throughout, Bright and Airy feel. The Full Basement adds an Additional 1900 square feet. Park yard backyard with Extra Large Deck, perfect for Entertaining. Situated on almost an Acre of property with Plenty of Privacy and a In Ground Heated Pool which is Fully Gated, Pool-house and much more! Come See for yourself!
